{
  "name": "[Core CRM] REC | Get EBS Accounts",
  "description": "[ECM-119250] - Create workato recipe to retreive ERP accounts from Rosetta Stone given a CRM account MDM ID and EBS Account Number\n\nThis recipe automates the process of searching for user account information in a Snowflake database based on input parameters received via an API request.\n- The process begins by receiving a request that specifies the type of search (e.g., by email or another identifier) and the corresponding search value.\n- It then executes a SQL query against the Snowflake database to retrieve relevant account details, including MDM party ID, country, account IDs, names, and statuses.\n- If the SQL query fails, an error message is returned indicating that the search service is temporarily busy.\n- Regardless of the outcome, the request details are logged for tracking purposes.\n- Finally, if the query is successful, the recipe returns the retrieved account information in a structured response format.",
  "version": 50,
  "private": true,
  "concurrency": 1,
  "version_comment": "ECM-119250 : Create workato recipe to retreive ERP accounts from Rosetta Stone given a CRM account MDM ID and EBS Account Number",
